Speaker B: Hello?
Speaker A: Hello, Hi, am I speaking with Min Joo Yang Wang?
Speaker B: Yes.
Speaker A: Hi, Min, how are you?
Speaker B: How are you? Who is calling?
Speaker A: Min, this is. I'm calling from Amber. I was calling regarding your accommodation.
Speaker B: Regarding my what? Sorry, I can't hear very well.
Speaker A: Yeah, can you hear me now?
Speaker B: Yeah, a little better.
Speaker A: Perfect. Min, this is Hussain. I'm calling from UCL portal for accommodation. Yeah, powered by Amber and I was calling regarding your accommodation.
Speaker B: Okay, yeah.
Speaker A: So could you please confirm, are you still looking for accommodation?
Speaker B: No, I'm no longer looking. I already secured a place. Yeah, sorry I wasn't able to get back to you earlier.
Speaker A: No worries on that. Can you please let me know where did you secure place? Like they booked a private accommodation or did you book a student accommodation?
Speaker B: Just through ucl.
Speaker A: Pardon?
Speaker B: Through ucl, one of the ones that they offer. Yeah, all.
Speaker A: Right, thank you so much.
Speaker B: Yeah, all right, thank you.
